results.content: This tutorial introduces the reader informally to the basic concepts and features of the Python language and system, a powerful and easy to learn language for scripting and rapid application development. results.title: Python (programming language)
results.content: Python is a high-level, general-purpose programming language. Its design philosophy emphasizes code readability with the use of significant indentation. Python is dynamically typed and garbage-collected. It supports multiple programming paradigms, including structured (particularly procedural), object-oriented and functional programming.
